{"tid":155589,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"《那年暑假，我去日本發了一場夢》","createTime":"2017-03-14T07:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T08:39:09.000Z","uid":23967,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5edcfc541a9a4dc43dced0e71d8f866517eadea5","tid":155589,"uid":23967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:04:41.000Z","msg":"因為之前工作太繁忙，所以完全無時間繼續出文，<br />\n加上好多舊登人轉咗過嚟，<br />\n決定寫多啲存貨先出，於是一推再推就到今日先出，<br />\n而家已經寫到50日，盡量每日行程分一至兩日出啦！<br />\n<br />\n《那年暑假，我去日本發了一場夢》<br />\n<br />\n9月1日，我完成了這80日旅程。<br />\n這三張全國JR Pass、150張特急指定席劵，<br />\n再加上這2張青春18車票，<br />\n成為我最心愛的手信。<br />\n<br />\n很多人都說，<br />\n大學畢業要來一場轟轟烈烈的旅行。<br />\n我同意，<br />\n所以才肯花了十個月時間計劃這個旅程。<br />\n人生只有這次機會有氣有力和有點點金錢，<br />\n要把握機會實在心中夢想，<br />\n否則到你出來社會工作後，<br />\n才發現這個夢想永遠都無法實現。<br />\n<br />\n我有兩個夢想︰<br />\n我想來一次鐵道旅行；<br />\n我很想登上富士山頂作為我畢業紀念。<br />\n於是，我想用火車環繞日本。<br />\n<br />\n第一個計劃是一個人50日環日本，<br />\n後來朋友建議一起上富士山，<br />\n又想去外島避世，<br />\n於是將計劃拉長至80日。<br />\n在日本尋找各種隱世景點，<br />\n做一次瘋狂事。<br />\n<br />\n由於這個旅程完全為自己而設，<br />\n很多大眾的景點和餐廳都無去，<br />\n但歡迎有問題、火車路線可以討論。"},{"pid":"b6255a2d3f7262c461a67b953ad417ea590466ee","tid":155589,"uid":23967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"Day 1 - 初開之前<br />\n<br />\n一個人前往機場，<br />\n雖然不是第一次獨遊，<br />\n因為太多未知事，<br />\n反而讓我卻更期待這80日。<br />\n晚上11時25分，香港國際機場，<br />\nHK Express UO624起飛。<br />\n<br />\n幸好我沒睡過頭，<br />\n隱約看到當時尚未開山的富士山頂和晨光第一線。<br />\n其實這程機票我早於上年八月已經買了，<br />\n還記得那時Megasale，<br />\n僅花330大元就可以坐凌晨機加窗口位。<br />\n去東京方向記得選左手邊窗口位，<br />\n很大機會看到富士山頂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Jsmya.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJsmya.md.jpg&h=18056188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n順便談談預備工作，<br />\n這次旅程頭56日用了3張JR全國Pass (21+21+14)。<br />\nJR全國Pass需要提早在香港預購，<br />\n3張加起約11000港幣。<br />\n酒店方面則盡量便宜，<br />\n基本用日本版樂天，再加Airbnb、<a href=\"http://Booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBooking.com&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2Buu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=c34cd8e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Booking.com</a>、email預約等<br />\n我對酒店卻沒太多要求，<br />\n能睡覺已經足夠。<br />\n<br />\n日本時間4:40，<br />\n羽田空港著陸。<br />\n落機氣溫還算溫暖， <br />\n太陽漸漸升起，<br />\n很久未試過在機場看日出，<br />\n感覺很特別，而且很美麗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/H8b7I.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FH8b7I.md.jpg&h=7c7fc34c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實這天在東京只是轉機，<br />\n10:30就要乘內陸機去北海道稚內。<br />\n稚內才是我鐵道之旅起點，<br />\n為甚麼選稚內﹖<br />\n因為它是最北的地點，<br />\n帶著很多神秘色彩&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n轉機要等近六小時，<br />\n而且6點連商店都未開，<br />\n於是走上國際大樓的觀光塔，<br />\n欣賞一下羽田空港的風景。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/H8Zq8.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FH8Zq8.md.jpg&h=c1f7622d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍藍天空，不冷不熱剛剛好，<br />\n而且周圍一個人都無，<br />\n讓自己休息一下，<br />\n順便收拾好心情，準備這80日挑戰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/H8fta.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FH8fta.md.jpg&h=c764a248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJR羽田中心要7:45才開門，<br />\n未夠7:30時，門口已經近三十人排隊。<br />\n我好像排第五，都要再等半小時才到我開票。<br />\n雖然買了三張JR Pass，但我先開頭兩張21日，<br />\n14日那張遲點再開。<br />\n<br />\n原來羽田這裡只准預約即日火車票，<br />\n由於我明天才開始用JR Pass，<br />\n所以只好去到稚內站才預約&hellip;&hellip;(幸好有綠窗口)<br />\n<br />\n開完JR Pass就搭免費巴士去國內線大樓，<br />\n大樓好像翻新過，而且光線很充足。<br />\nANA國內線很多，<br />\n所以Checkin要排很長隊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/H8wut.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FH8wut.md.jpg&h=eaf1f9f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/H8M0G.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FH8M0G.md.jpg&h=ce9f9f05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n告示板寫去稚內飛機要再三確認風速能否准許如期飛行，<br />\n代表稚內天氣非常不好，<br />\n天文台又寫僅得10度，<br />\n我都抹了一額汗&hellip;&hellip;幸好最後順利登機。<br />\n<br />\n寄完行李後又走到樓頂拍拍飛機，<br />\n雖然完全不懂飛機型號，<br />\n但配合對出東京灣實在美麗，<br />\n和ANA飛機好襯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/H8jRz.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FH8jRz.md.jpg&h=27052624&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/H8oMy.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FH8oMy.md.jpg&h=dd4481bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/H8dtp.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FH8dtp.md.jpg&h=c8400c08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要去501號閘口，<br />\n代表要搭巴士去機場中央上機，<br />\n想不到原來都頗多人坐，<br />\n幾乎全滿，而且很多老人家，<br />\n後來到稚內才知道有火車旅行團。<br />\n用6日時間坐火車由稚內去鹿兒島，<br />\n想想都辛苦&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/H8nQP.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FH8nQP.md.jpg&h=f4114911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/H85sb.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FH85sb.md.jpg&h=9e5e7679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/H8lZu.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FH8lZu.md.jpg&h=12147bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlsXF.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlsXF.md.jpg&h=e277ff2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上10時45分，羽田空港，<br />\nANA NH571起飛。<br />\n110分鐘機程，沒有飛機餐，<br />\n只有一杯果汁和糖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlyMq.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlyMq.md.jpg&h=4dc25d7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12時45分，稚內空港，<br />\n在朦朧間睡醒，原來已經到達北海道稚內市。<br />\n北海道，我來了！"},{"pid":"3e4f79de457b3a4067e767c13b5efd8c5bc5275e","tid":155589,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:30:14.000Z","msg":"留名正皮支持"},{"pid":"eeb03b8d3b7de924f2e9d1d996e255f69fe021c9","tid":155589,"uid":23967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:31:18.000Z","msg":"稚內空港跑道很短，<br />\n飛機降落後要U-Turn到停機坪，<br />\n第一次有這種體驗，很有趣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Hl2vH.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHl2vH.md.jpg&h=211a94e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n稚內空港是地區機場，<br />\n一日只有三班航機，<br />\n全部都是來往東京羽田。<br />\n客運大樓只有一條輸送帶，<br />\n行李也很快就噴出來。<br />\n而大堂出閘的地方亦僅可容納一百人左右，<br />\n出閘旁邊就是入閘口，<br />\n很地方味道的空港。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlO0U.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlO0U.md.jpg&h=66fe13c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n踏出空港，冷空氣瞬間捲入身體，<br />\n幸好先在東京穿heattech打底，<br />\n6月中的北海道還屬春天，<br />\n經常落雨，氣溫只有12度。<br />\n本來想直接去宗谷岬，<br />\n但因為下大雨，決定先到民宿Check-in和午餐。<br />\n<br />\n稚內空港離市區差不多20公里，<br />\n一般都會搭巴士(600 yen)到火車站，<br />\n巴士班次配合航班時間，<br />\n所以不用擔心要等很耐食風云云。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlHO2.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlHO2.md.jpg&h=34bc88a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來在網絡看到稚內青年旅舍，<br />\n但不知為何不能預約，<br />\n決定改為住民宿，<br />\n旅館以木以 &ndash; 4860 yen，<br />\n日式民宿，每間房都很大，而且很方便。<br />\n老闆和老闆娘已經是六十已過，<br />\n但依舊笑容滿面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlJKQ.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlJKQ.md.jpg&h=9ed0f6a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCheck-in後放低行李便去吃午餐，<br />\n雖然拉麵不算特別出色，<br />\n但冷天氣中吃一碗熱騰騰拉麵倍感開心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlNbT.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlNbT.md.jpg&h=aaa6d114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出發去防波堤之前，<br />\n先去最北車站拍攝即將離站的特急「利尻」，<br />\n剛才一班公公婆婆就立刻登上這車去札幌，<br />\n開始它們的六天縱貫之旅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlERx.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlERx.md.jpg&h=d5c045a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlDVa.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlDVa.md.jpg&h=deeb5d17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlVat.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlVat.md.jpg&h=b5a0f984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n稚內 &ndash; 旭川稱為宗谷本線，<br />\n全長近260km，<br />\n2017年3月JR時刻表改點後，<br />\n只有特急「宗谷」會直到札幌，<br />\n另一款特急「利尻」(Sarobetsu)只會去到旭川。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HltQV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHltQV.jpg&h=d1769609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「利尻」(サロベツ)一日只有一個來回班次，<br />\n使用舊車Kiha 183行駛，<br />\n列車名取自稚內市對出的利尻島，<br />\n好天還可以看到利尻富士，很是壯觀。<br />\n其餘兩個特急班次為特急「超級宗谷」(現為「宗谷)，<br />\n使用較新的Kiha 261行駛。<br />\n<br />\n列車離開後，<br />\n整個車站瞬間變得寧靜。<br />\n去窗口劃了明天要坐的特急超級宗谷2號及利尻號，<br />\n與及28日後要坐的Sunrise瀨戶號。<br />\n經過15分鐘指手劃腳再加有限日文解釋，<br />\n終於收到這張車票！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JsBzj.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJsBzj.md.jpg&h=d8b4aafc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那一刻真是興奮得難以形容，<br />\n至於為甚麼我會這樣，<br />\n遲一點再解釋解釋。<br />\n<br />\n出發前往稚內防坡堤，<br />\n長近400米的防波堤長年擋風擋浪，<br />\n保護內港船隻安全之餘，<br />\n亦非常適合拍照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlS5s.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlS5s.md.jpg&h=bec93e67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlaAD.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlaAD.md.jpg&h=fff18217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜天氣不佳，路上僅得小貓三數隻，<br />\n80年代這裡有鐵道直出海邊，<br />\n將車輛或貨物運上船到北方四島。<br />\n今天北方四島已變成俄羅斯領土，<br />\n北海道鐵道亦以不復昔日興盛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlrM8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlrM8.jpg&h=53fde5a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlhvI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlhvI.jpg&h=afef3b82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9605fa03269a6cfde44548d856364c0438d0712","tid":155589,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:34:07.000Z","msg":"80日點記得哂每日啲行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a3ed8949624c97a10da78d12bb64a809c826e6","tid":155589,"uid":23967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>80日點記得哂每日啲行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有寫日記同瘋狂影相<br />\n其實好易記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da12640ea1180909575eb3df3a2a54a242092179","tid":155589,"uid":86456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等睇"},{"pid":"62f0c6ec50d4d650855e29bd7b9becb51e29118c","tid":155589,"uid":20011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T08:16:24.000Z","msg":"80日可以正接出書<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb263f260689c137bfefbe2607d03c6e98aba04","tid":155589,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9431f03eabd79428fccd8f536955d22ff703edea","tid":155589,"uid":23967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:05:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>80日可以正接出書<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都有興趣 希望有書商/出版社睇中啦<br />\n而家寫左大約50日大約70000-80000字左右"},{"pid":"e1cbbdea5e891f74359ebab0000024c048287312","tid":155589,"uid":23967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T12:36:46.000Z","msg":"差不多4時，<br />\n回到車站準備乘巴士去宗谷岬，<br />\n起初以為路程很短，<br />\n但想不到竟然要近一小時車程，<br />\n坐到睡著了&hellip;..<br />\n可惜不好天，否則整條沿海路應該很漂亮，<br />\n而且還可以望到北方四島。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Hl9OA.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHl9OA.md.jpg&h=341e1957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來到宗谷岬，<br />\n幸好停了雨，<br />\n亦幸好只是留在這裡40分鐘，<br />\n因為只有一塊最北之地紀念碑，<br />\n連少少博物館也無。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlKQj.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlKQj.md.jpg&h=ae22e6e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過附近很多東西也標榜自己是最北甚麼甚麼，<br />\n旅館、觀光中心、餐廳，連廁所都有。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlTzN.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlTzN.md.jpg&h=62b316a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間也有點難熬，終於等到回程巴士，<br />\n其實車費很貴，一來一回居然要2600yen，<br />\n但一場來到，唯有含淚付費。<br />\n<br />\n晚上七時，空城。<br />\n街上一個人也沒有，<br />\n除了便利店外，連餐廳都無，<br />\n唯有買便當回民宿吃。<br />\n<br />\n民宿老闆爺爺實在太好人，<br />\n幫我開水之餘，<br />\n更問我明天坐幾點車，<br />\n我答七時的特急，<br />\n他叫我六時起床載我到車站。<br />\n霎時感到很不好意思，<br />\n居然要他這麼早起床，<br />\n用兩分鐘車我去車站。<br />\n但日本人就是這樣，<br />\n招待會全套做好。<br />\n<br />\n都是早點睡覺好了。<br />\n<br />\nDay 1‧完"},{"pid":"dfe75b5c88c84fb33a2204d7d046d780cbb919bc","tid":155589,"uid":35566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T12:51:03.000Z","msg":"全程使咗幾錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aeaa772898cea752bab245166ae15488ae957e1","tid":155589,"uid":51905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T12:58:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全程使咗幾錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想問+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92613fa7291ae6f98e6c430af09e498a9dc5f7c","tid":155589,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T13:18:35.000Z","msg":"等睇爛尾"},{"pid":"7e8125eb5001ade408f642d17c366f2d5143db36","tid":155589,"uid":23967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T13:45:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等睇爛尾</blockquote><br />\n今次唔啦<br />\n存貨好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34db9b7b6b5d78b55ecfd7a47094be2b10162665","tid":155589,"uid":23967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T13:45:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>全程使咗幾錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想問+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大約48000港紙"},{"pid":"6dcd3bf017a0eaa84c873547a0f2cadce2a9c16e","tid":155589,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T13:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等睇爛尾</blockquote><br />\n等睇爛尾x2"},{"pid":"c1ca41656afa11c07281443ee65088a6f4be378a","tid":155589,"uid":23967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:26:38.000Z","msg":"Day 2 &ndash; 初開<br />\n<br />\n未夠六時我已經自然醒過來，<br />\n很精神，很興奮，很期待，<br />\n只有旅行才會有這種情況。<br />\n<br />\n簡單梳洗後收拾好行李就離開民宿，<br />\n多謝民宿爺爺車我去稚內站，<br />\n那管只是兩分鐘車程。<br />\n在日本拒絕反而是一種不禮貌，<br />\n與其尷尬，不如大方接受。<br />\n<br />\n到達車站時，六時半也未到，<br />\n去附近行了一圈，再買點早餐就入閘，<br />\n這時候車也到站了。<br />\n下次來稚內一定會再去禮文和利尻島！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlYAg.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlYAg.md.jpg&h=bdf55583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Hl0Vp.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHl0Vp.md.jpg&h=cbde500e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾年前稚內站翻新過，變成單線月台，<br />\n以一日只有數班車的小總站來說已經夠了。<br />\n趁上車之前拍下少許最北站的標誌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlBzb.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlBzb.md.jpg&h=fad772b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Hleam.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHleam.md.jpg&h=daa8822b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlfWF.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlfWF.md.jpg&h=39cb7592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7點正，特急「超級宗谷2號」札幌行出發，<br />\n意味著56日的鐵道之旅正式開始！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Hl3oG.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHl3oG.md.jpg&h=fec56eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlmyP.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlmyP.md.jpg&h=6941cc5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlkoU.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlkoU.md.jpg&h=5bd6f7dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特急「超級宗谷2號」(現「宗谷)由Kiha 261系4輛編成，<br />\n來往稚內 &ndash; 札幌，全程需時近5小時。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlLHq.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlLHq.md.jpg&h=cf377453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚在旭川住，<br />\n到達旭川前先去宗谷本線最大城市 &ndash; 名寄。<br />\n這程車要坐2小時40分鐘，<br />\n不知是否時間太早，整程乘客不多。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HlQYH.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlQYH.md.jpg&h=f88666fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Hlccx.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHlccx.md.jpg&h=49d7abe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經常聽到有人說北海道太大，<br />\n究竟大的程度去到哪裡﹖<br />\n1.\t聽說北海道的牛比人還要多，頗有趣。<br />\n2.\t由鐵道來說，將所有日本私鐵線放到北海道地圖，都只是佔一半多一點。<br />\n再不明白就自己想像了吧&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n沒有影太多相，享受風景為主，<br />\n兩個半小時的車程很快就過，<br />\n來到沿線最大城市 &ndash; 名寄！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Hl5YI.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHl5YI.md.jpg&h=f74209f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所謂最大城市，<br />\n其實都不過是札幌人口50分之一，<br />\n路上依然是一個人都沒有。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPhmm.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPhmm.md.jpg&h=b12bcbdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本還是陰天，怎料突然放晴，<br />\n好好把握機會去第一個景點 - キマロキ編成SL排雪車。<br />\n由名寄站前往北國紀念館要步行15分鐘，<br />\n這輛是前名寄本線的專用除雪車，<br />\n1996年北國紀念館開幕後就一直放在這裡對外展示。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPsfN.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPsfN.md.jpg&h=8c099f7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"801a226e5f2f4ab1a3f1e95488a6c8d956a6ed13","tid":155589,"uid":23967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPi9A.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPi9A.md.jpg&h=df466e3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這輛火車早在七十年代已經退役，<br />\n當年排雪還要靠蒸汽火車，可想而知效率如何地低，<br />\n於是國鐵更換成柴油機場，加快剷雪速度。<br />\n特大的齒輪、車身略高，裡面還有大窩輪，<br />\n但因為極大的蜘蛛網，免得不安不貼相吧&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JP1r3.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJP1r3.md.jpg&h=6b7072ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JP2mt.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJP2mt.md.jpg&h=574560c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPEUg.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPEUg.md.jpg&h=b5f3f829&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天氣放晴，氣溫上升至20度左右，<br />\n加上柔和的微風，真是很很很很舒服。<br />\n而且影出來的效果也非常好！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPO8M.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPO8M.md.jpg&h=5d6224ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPH3y.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPH3y.md.jpg&h=c930be72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JsjUm.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJsjUm.md.jpg&h=7257636e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一輛火車都影了差不多一個半小時，<br />\n是時候回到車站，<br />\n再來兩張Wide shot和情景吧！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPXfb.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPXfb.md.jpg&h=5438763b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPal6.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPal6.md.jpg&h=f684d73b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一條大直路看不到盡頭，<br />\n就像我未知終點一樣，<br />\n雖然有點不安，但很有挑戰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JP6ru.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJP6ru.md.jpg&h=28fea71e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n回車站途中見到老爺車，<br />\n用電話拍就算。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Js5YU.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJs5YU.md.jpg&h=cb0e66f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到車站前吃個午餐，<br />\n當然要吃我最愛的吉列定食。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPDdF.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPDdF.md.jpg&h=a0fb0bd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JsuJF.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJsuJF.md.jpg&h=3a116a9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吃過午餐又是時候出發，<br />\n不過還是未到旭川，<br />\n我早一晚在宗谷線挑了一個小站，<br />\n在那裡過一段獨自一人的時光。<br />\n於是，我跳上了這班一時正發車的快速「なよろ」(快速名寄)。<br />\n用車是Kiha40，一款非常舊的柴油車。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPzJU.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPzJU.md.jpg&h=9b704063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JP93q.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJP93q.md.jpg&h=1491fa36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPTwH.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPTwH.md.jpg&h=3d0cb900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n起動很慢，引擎聲響徹雲霄。<br />\n北海道很多單卡火車都可以開窗，<br />\n享受外面的涼風。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPG1x.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPG1x.md.jpg&h=c3f52a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPRTV.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPRTV.md.jpg&h=0ec68018&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n約半小時車程，來到劍淵站，<br />\n剛巧和對面另一輛Kiha 40會車。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPVk2.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPVk2.md.jpg&h=48cfa641&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9456c7d14472cafc45d83fe3708cb1c0804f3f65","tid":155589,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:27:18.000Z","msg":"你依家係重POST定接住落?"},{"pid":"87885a1bedad30ed7adfa4a60f2fd92835c96f57","tid":155589,"uid":90000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:40:34.000Z","msg":"強貼留名"},{"pid":"115fd90f405d2b5cc13c653e54ff2b99155e93db","tid":155589,"uid":23967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:59:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你依家係重POST定接住落?</blockquote><br />\n重Post<br />\n因為之前啲相在imgur死哂<br />\n同埋想完整啲 所以由頭黎過"},{"pid":"29cca23dd2451d4341216f3127f740dfc28a5729","tid":155589,"uid":23967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強貼留名</blockquote><br />\n見到你個名都想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27235eeccfb1de4b2e257ade40422f03df907c3b","tid":155589,"uid":23967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:18:37.000Z","msg":"劍淵，一個名寄本線上寂寂無名的車站，<br />\n看著那輛老爺車慢慢加速離我而去，<br />\n回名寄的火車要兩小時後才到，<br />\n一股刺激感渾然而生，<br />\n究竟在時間表亂選的車站是怎麼一回事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPYlQ.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPYlQ.md.jpg&h=d2116ac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPqBs.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPqBs.md.jpg&h=149cccaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，這一刻我肚痛，<br />\n問士多姨姨才知原來站內有洗手間。<br />\n一入去，嘩屌，不得了，<br />\n一個小車站居然有這樣舒適的洗手間，<br />\n馬桶比某些酒店更舒適，<br />\n沒有臭味、全自動、廁所板會發熱，還有潔淨功能。<br />\n舒服得不想離開&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n解決大事後在站附近閒逛，<br />\n車站待合室設有暖爐，<br />\n現在當然不用開，<br />\n但冬天恐怕溫度低至-20度，<br />\n作為香港人都真不明他們如何生存。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPC6T.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPC6T.md.jpg&h=fb52b411&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車站附近也是民居為主，<br />\n附近有一間美術館和JA貨倉，<br />\n美術館好像無開，但左邊的壁畫很美。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPWND.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPWND.md.jpg&h=035c4b9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJA貨倉用紅磚建造，<br />\n很古典很有味道，<br />\n它有一道門開了，驚現裡面是一個個成人般高的大袋，<br />\n究竟裡面是甚麼！！﹖﹖<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPm38.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPm38.md.jpg&h=70a780bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPBwI.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPBwI.md.jpg&h=e8601fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行了半小時又回到車站，<br />\n索性睡在月台上，<br />\n不熱不冷的溫度配上微風，<br />\n讓人忘記煩憂，和大自然融為一體。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Jy1pp.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJy1pp.md.jpg&h=abd31403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JyEiz.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJyEiz.md.jpg&h=a2808df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JytDP.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJytDP.md.jpg&h=9ac2b417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拍下照，睡下覺，<br />\n下班車即將進站，<br />\n這架Kiha 54系列車和剛才不同，<br />\n不鏽鋼車身，車頭很有日本味道，<br />\n主力行走道北和道東地段，<br />\n之後日子經常遇上，<br />\n但它一點也不好坐。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPbTj.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPbTj.md.jpg&h=2bcfb4ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPZ2a.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPZ2a.md.jpg&h=92fbc402&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKiha 54亦可以開窗，<br />\n中途在某些木板車站停站，很過癮！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JyNSu.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJyNSu.md.jpg&h=28af18f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又回到名寄，<br />\n在車站外買了一杯雪糕便準備上特急到旭川。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPekA.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPekA.md.jpg&h=95bc1352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次乘特急「利尻」，<br />\n車頭車尾款式不同。<br />\n可能中午關係，客量頗多，<br />\n我只能坐走廊位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPkPN.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPkPN.md.jpg&h=9919792e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPp6M.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPp6M.md.jpg&h=945acfbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKiha 183系很舊，<br />\n車廂內完全沒有電子顯示屏幕，<br />\n全人手報站，<br />\n聽說還有一至兩年就會退役，<br />\n要坐和影多一點了！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPLB3.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPLB3.md.jpg&h=82815814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPQjt.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPQjt.md.jpg&h=90e43fda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五時半到達旭川站，<br />\n翻新後的旭川站高架化起來，<br />\n整個站瞬間前衛又時尚。<br />\n但用了很多木造裝飾，<br />\n感覺又變得文青&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPxxy.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPxxy.md.jpg&h=8fb840a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPM2p.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPM2p.md.jpg&h=34f77f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPjPb.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPjPb.md.jpg&h=c809bdbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPo4z.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPo4z.md.jpg&h=ea477c51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n趁那邊的特急「超級神威」(Super Kamui)和「利尻」未離開之際，<br />\n拍下一輛我最愛的車型 &ndash; 789系<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPgNg.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPgNg.md.jpg&h=1b5b4f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPwCG.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPwCG.md.jpg&h=b76f6786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旭川站和札幌站相比，<br />\n人流少很多，<br />\n很喜歡這種不擠逼的感覺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPnh6.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPnh6.md.jpg&h=d2f23971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JPuBu.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJPuBu.md.jpg&h=3c906c7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚餐去到附近一間頗出名的拉麵店，<br />\n由於我不是特別愛吃之人，<br />\n所以貼一張相大家再去找找就好了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JyaEU.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJyaEU.md.jpg&h=d91841f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚住在Guesthouse，<br />\n不算貴，而且老闆娘好好人，<br />\n幫忙預約一間民宿，<br />\n因為它沒有email和網上預約，<br />\n只能來到日本打電話，<br />\n十分感謝她義不容辭幫了我大忙！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JySqm.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJySqm.md.jpg&h=3bbbbeb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/JyF7F.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FJyF7F.md.jpg&h=e870b1ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚放下相機，<br />\n在旭川車站和大街附近散策，<br />\n明天將去尋找面臨廢線的最後風光。<br />\n<br />\nDay 2‧完"},{"pid":"3ea2909c3b7bf5865ac617982c9c6bba05382bba","tid":155589,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T01:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53f4eeb4e9f626dfc05f027eeb9dee6be31b923","tid":155589,"uid":51940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T02:31:54.000Z","msg":"留名 <br />\n樓主用乜相機 好wide，執得又靚啲色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb609232130e20e72fd757639c9f6a4faceb5d74","tid":155589,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor